                     </persName>
                  , part of a box, value 6 d. thirty books, value 2 s. seven pounds in monies numbered, and seven-pence, and twenty bank notes, value one pound each, the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18091101-72-victim593" type="victimName">
                           Matthew 
                           Butler
